---

## 5. Your Own Governance

A guild is a sub-cooperative within the cooperative. Your guild votes on:
- How to spend the treasury
- Which theme represents you
- Which banner flies on your page
- Which initiatives to support with collective voting power
- How to welcome new members

Your guild. Your rules. Your vote.

---

## 6. Your Path to Captain

Starting a guild IS a Captain pathway. The Guild Leader is a Captain of their professional domain.

The Cold Start Hub has six paths. Food. Manufacturing. Service. Local Business. Guild. Tribe. All lead to Captain. All start at 10 members.

You don't need to sell anything to become a Captain. You can organize a Guild instead.

