## Quick Reference -- Steward Cheat Sheet

| Scenario | Action | Marks Impact |
|---|---|---|
| Clean week, no stamps | Escrow holds, Marks stay with member | 0 forfeited |
| Stamp filed, not contested, upheld | Marks transfer to cooperative fund | Up to 10 forfeited |
| Stamp filed, contested, Steward upholds | Marks transfer to cooperative fund | Up to 10 forfeited |
| Stamp filed, contested, Steward dismisses | Marks remain with member | 0 forfeited |
| 3 valid stamps in one month | Auto-trigger Steward review | Max 30/month cap |
| Member balance < 10 Marks for pledge | Agreement enters probation status | Notification sent |

